== 製作 ==

=== 編劇 ===
基於《[[X戰警_(電影)|X戰警]]》的評價及財務的成功，使[[二十世紀福斯|二十世紀福斯]]立刻開始計畫續集。從2000年11月開始<ref name=second/uncanny>''The Second Uncanny Issue of X-Men: Making X2'' Documentary, 2003, [[20th_Century_Fox|20th Century Fox]]</ref>，[[布萊恩·辛格|布萊恩·辛格]]研究了X戰警漫畫系列的各種故事情節<ref name=next>{{cite news|author=Brown, Scott|title=EW tracks the evolution of ''X2''|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2003-05-09|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,449160,00.html|accessdate=2008-02-18|archivedate=2015-05-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150512084027/http://www.ew.com/article/2003/05/02/ew-tracks-evolution-x2|deadurl=no}}</ref>，表示想研究「人類觀點，那種煽動戰爭和恐怖主義的盲目狂怒」<ref>{{cite news|title= Bunches of Marvel|publisher= (Comics2Film column; seventh item down) Comic Book Resources|date= 2002-08-14|url= http://www.comicbookresources.com/columns/index.cgi?column=comics2film&article=1397|accessdate= 2007-05-01|archivedate= 2015-08-29|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20150829220433/http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=14185|deadurl= no}}</ref>。且辛格指出，電影需要一名「人類惡棍」<ref name=second/uncanny>''The Second Uncanny Issue of X-Men: Making X2'' Documentary, 2003, [[20th_Century_Fox|20th Century Fox]]</ref>。製片人{{link-en|艾維·亞拉|Avi Arad}}宣布計畫於2002年11月發行<ref>{{cite news|title=''Fantastic Four'': The Comedy?!|publisher=IGN|date=2001-04-28|url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/057/057515p1.html|accessdate=2008-03-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227175120/http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/04/28/fantastic-four-the-comedy|archivedate=2014-02-27|deadurl=no}}</ref>，而[[大衛·海特|大衛·海特]]和[[塞克·潘|塞克·潘]]被聘請為電影撰寫獨立的劇本<ref name=xcons>{{cite news|author=Stax|title=Lauren Shuler Donner Talks ''X-Men 2'' and ''Constantine''|publisher=IGN|date=2001-06-15|url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/300/300581p1.html|accessdate=2008-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090929083708/http://movies.ign.com/articles/300/300581p1.html|archive-date=2009-09-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>，再結合彼此認為最好的要素結合成一部最終的劇本<ref>{{cite news|author=Stax|title="Closing In" on ''X-Men 2''|publisher=IGN|date=2001-11-07|url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/315/315905p1.html|accessdate=2008-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070905214129/http://movies.ign.com/articles/315/315905p1.html|archive-date=2007-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[麥可·道格堤|麥可·道格堤]]和{{link-en|丹·哈里斯|Dan Harris (screenwriter)}}在2002年2月被雇用改寫海特和潘的劇本<ref>{{cite news|author=Grove, Martin A.|title=Fox's ''X2'' marks spot as presummer starts May 2|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2003-04-11|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/search/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1863776|accessdate=2007-04-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930201512/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/search/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1863776|archivedate=2007-09-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>，拒絕了撰寫《{{link-en|下一個就是你：血腥瑪麗|Urban Legends: Bloody Mary}}》的劇本的機會<ref>{{cite news|author=Stax|title=Magneto Escapes!|publisher=IGN|date=2002-05-08|url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/358/358779p1.html|accessdate=2008-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081210181549/http://movies.ign.com/articles/358/358779p1.html|archive-date=2008-12-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{link-en|天使（漫威漫畫）|Warren Worthington III|天使}}與[[野獸_(漫畫)|野獸]]早期出現在草案中，但最後被刪除了<ref name=Legacy>{{cite news|author=Worley, Rob|title=''X-Men 2'' [first of two Worley articles of this title]|publisher=(Comics2 Film column; third item down) Comic Book Resources|date=2002-10-23|url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/columns/index.cgi?column=comics2film&article=1467|accessdate=2008-02-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150501122251/http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=14255|archivedate=2015-05-01|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
製片人{{link-en|羅倫·舒勒·唐納|Lauren Shuler Donner}}曾希望在2002年3月開始拍攝<ref name=xcons/>，但是直到2002年6月17日才在[[溫哥華|溫哥華]]開拍<ref name="greg"/>，直到11月才結束。且劇組在38個地點使用了64個不同的位置<ref name=X2>{{cite news | last = Worley | first = Rob | title = ''X-Men 2'' [second of two Worley articles of this title] | publisher = (Comics2Film column) Comic Book Resources | date = 2002-10-30 | url = http://www.comicbookresources.com/columns/index.cgi?column=comics2film&article=1475 | accessdate = 2008-02-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20040121010054/http://www.comicbookresources.com/columns/index.cgi?column=comics2film&article=1475 | archivedate = 2004-01-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 發行 ==

=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度86%，基於235條評論，平均分為7.5/10<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/x2_xmen_united/|title=X2: X-Men United|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2015-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711082033/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/x2_xmen_united/|archive-date=2015-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到68分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/x2|title=X2: X-Men United (2003): Reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2008-03-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699xRyZy9?url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/x2|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，收穫普遍好評。

=== 票房 ===
[[北美|北美]]地區在2003年5月2日首映，上映後首週末在3,749家劇院累積了85,558,731美元的票房，最終北美票房高達214,949,694美元，其他地區收入192,761,855美元，全球票房總計407,711,549美元，成為一個票房上的成功，因票房較成本高了三倍<ref name="BOM"/>。電影同時在93個國家首次亮相，為當時最大的北美及國際開業紀錄<ref>{{cite news|last=Linder|first=Brian|url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/400/400483p1.html|title=This Weekend at the Movies: ''X2'' Debuts|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2003-05-02|accessdate=2008-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081213002614/http://movies.ign.com/articles/400/400483p1.html|archive-date=2008-12-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，《X戰警2》是考慮[[通貨膨脹|通貨膨脹]]中，漫威改編電影票房第13高的電影<ref>{{cite web|title=Marvel Comics Movies|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=marvelcomics.htm|accessdate=2008-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131026111510/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=marvelcomics.htm|archive-date=2013-10-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是[[2003年電影|2003年]]票房第六高的電影<ref>{{cite web|title=2003 Yearly Box Office Results|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2003&p=.htm|accessdate=2008-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071001050235/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2003&p=.htm|archive-date=2007-10-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

